<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.IRenderer.WindowSystemInfoBase.WindowSystemType" Title="WindowSystemType enumeration" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IRenderer.WindowSystemInfoBase">WindowSystemInfoBase</PageRef> ->
    WindowSystemType
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>WindowSystemType</TypeRef> enumeration identifies the platform window system described by a concrete <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IRenderer.WindowSystemInfoBase">WindowSystemInfoBase</PageRef> derived structure.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Members">
    <EnumMemberList>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="Headless">
        Identifies a headless renderer environment with no operating system window system.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="Win32">
        Identifies the Microsoft Windows Win32 window system.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="Xlib">
        Identifies the Xlib window system on Linux and compatible platforms.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="XCB">
        Identifies the XCB window system on Linux and compatible platforms.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="Wayland">
        Identifies the Wayland window system on Linux and compatible platforms.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="AppKit">
        Identifies the AppKit window system on macOS.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
    </EnumMemberList>
  </Section>
